~$ git clone git://github.com/ignovak/vimrc ~/.vim
~$ ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc

Russian spelling
~$ wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/klen/.vim/raw/master/spell/ru.utf-8.spl https://github.com/klen/.vim/raw/master/spell/ru.utf-8.sug -P ~/.vim/spell/

Inconsolata font: http://levien.com/type/myfonts/inconsolata.html
